ejecta must be $\\lesssim 10^{-3}-10^{-2} E_{\\rm rot}$. We\ndiscuss the different diagnostics available to identify magnetar-driven\nkilonovae in serendipitous observations and draw parallels to other potential\nmagnetar-driven explosions, such as superluminous supernovae and broad-line\nsupernovae Ic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 May 2022 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2022 10:31:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
