ke connections over the sample.\nThese results underline the need for caution in over-interpreting the\nsignificance of these strings and their role in understanding the star\nformation history of the Milky Way.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 May 2022 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2022 18:17:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
