y of activities will inspire faculty\nmembers and students at colleges and perhaps high schools to imagine new\npossibilities for developing communities of people in science that might not\notherwise be able to exist.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 May 2022 22:12:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2022 15:54:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2023 20:23:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
