oirs. We conclude with providing an outlook in this\nvibrant research field, with emphasis on the outstanding open questions\npertaining to the underlying physics along with noting the advances in\nexploiting this switching process in technological applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 May 2022 05:54:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
